70.9	Requiem_for_a_Dream	Requiem for a Dream	Requiem for a Dream is a 2000 drama film directed by Darren Aronofsky and starring Ellen Burstyn, Jared Leto, Marlon Wayans and Jennifer Connelly. The film is based on the novel of the same name by Hubert Selby, Jr., with whom Aronofsky wrote the screenplay. Burstyn was nominated for an Academy Award for Best Actress for her performance. The film was screened out of competition at the 2000 Cannes Film Festival.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/9/92/Requiem_for_a_dream.jpg/220px-Requiem_for_a_dream.jpg
